omeprazole (Prilosec), and lansoprazole (Prevacid). Be sure to let your doctor and pharmacist know that you are taking these medications before you start taking doxycycline. Do not start any of these medications while taking doxycycline without discussing with your healthcare provider. be aware that antacids containing magnesium, aluminum, or calcium, calcium supplements, iron products, and laxatives containing magnesium interfere with doxycycline, making it less effective. 
